"title": "5769: behaviour",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5769",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A person's actions or way of life. Good behaviour will not earn salvation, but believers must practise good behaviour in accordance with Scripture as evidence of their conversion. Scripture stresses that bad behaviour is inconsistent with Christian faith and urges believers to mend their ways.</p>\n<h2>Examples of good behaviour</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:22\">GEN 6:22</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:6\">LUK 1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:24\">GEN 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:3\">2KI 18:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:8\">JOB 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:47\">JHN 1:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:3\">3JN 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:5-3John1:6\">3JN 1:5–1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:12\">3JN 1:12</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of bad behaviour</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:30\">1KI 16:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:8\">GEN 4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:5\">GEN 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:3\">1SA 25:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:14\">2TI 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:9-3John1:10\">3JN 1:9–1:10</a></p>\n<h2>Good behaviour towards God is commanded</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:2-Exod20:11\">EXO 20:2–20:11</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:6-Deut5:15\">DEU 5:6–5:15</a></p>\n<h3>Obedience to God's word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:2\">PSA 1:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:7-Ps19:11\">PSA 19:7–19:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:1-Ps119:4\">PSA 119:1–119:4</a></p>\n<h2>Good behaviour towards other people is commanded</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:12\">1PE 2:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:12-Exod20:17\">EXO 20:12–20:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:16-Deut5:21\">DEU 5:16–5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps15:1-Ps15:5\">PSA 15:1–15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:2\">PRO 12:2</a> <em><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:1-Prov31:31\">Pr 10:1–31:31</a> contains much wisdom concerning good and bad behaviour</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:21-Matt5:24\">MAT 5:21–5:24</a></p>\n<h2>Good behaviour does not earn salvation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:20\">ROM 3:20</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:5\">TIT 3:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:15-Gal2:16\">GAL 2:15–2:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:8-Eph2:9\">EPH 2:8–2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:9\">PHP 3:9</a></p>\n<h2>Good behaviour confirms a believer's profession of faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:14-Jas2:19\">JAS 2:14–2:19</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:5-2Pet1:11\">2PE 1:5–1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:16-Matt7:20\">MAT 7:16–7:20</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:43-Luke6:45\">LUK 6:43–6:45</a></p>\n<h3>Obedience to Jesus Christ and his teachings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24-Matt7:25\">MAT 7:24–7:25</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:47-Luke6:48\">LUK 6:47–6:48</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:15\">JHN 14:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:23\">JHN 14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:10\">JHN 15:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:16\">COL 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>A believer has died to sin and is alive to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:11-Rom6:14\">ROM 6:11–6:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:2\">ROM 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:19\">ROM 6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:16\">GAL 5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:24-Gal5:25\">GAL 5:24–5:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:22-Eph4:24\">EPH 4:22–4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:1\">COL 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:5\">COL 3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:9-Col3:10\">COL 3:9–3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:5-1Thess5:8\">1TH 5:5–5:8</a></p>",
